{"tid":907540,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"HTC U12+ 是最後！向高階旗艦說再見","createTime":"2018-11-19T00:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T05:19:50.000Z","uid":23677,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"f09d514d7915b533192e485ba79525399b1dc3b3","tid":907540,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T00:58:50.000Z","msg":"過去數年 HTC 的智能手機業務成績每況愈下，HTC 決定聚焦於高階手機產品，希望能夠保住利潤。可惜最新上市的 HTC U12+ 銷售情況並不理想，消息指 HTC 可能會再一次改變出機策略。最新消息指，HTC 已經取消了 HTC U13+，甚至是 2019 年上半年的所有旗艦機計劃。<br />\n<br />\n有指 HTC 打算改為在明年春季末段，推出中階手機；不過至今還未知道 HTC 打算將手機以什麼價位上市，而手機的規格和設計亦是一個謎。雖然明年上半年沒有高階旗艦，U13+ 亦被取消，外國傳媒指 HTC 還是會有另一手準備在明年下半年推出，不過這樣的話就很大機會要面對 Galaxy Note 10、新 iPhone、新 Pixel 手機等強勁的對手。<br />\n<br />\n現時 HTC 的全球市佔率已經跌至少於 1%，HTC 似乎要好好想想前面的路該如何走，方能夠力挽狂瀾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4542/211883/1/1/129625\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4542%2F211883%2F1%2F1%2F129625&d=pZBVOThsalqHuy22W8pBzMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=cd461e9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4542/211883/1/1/129625</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紅姨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab1ee61261020afe548990fadb258827f63ab47","tid":907540,"uid":39335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab066a61022f3d4c3f1c5e118af1d4aa3279e6d4","tid":907540,"uid":60831,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:15:39.000Z","msg":"執柒咗佢算啦"},{"pid":"702254f42a8a02f52df9920a1878d9f4a295bc9c","tid":907540,"uid":117958,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:15:50.000Z","msg":"其實可以重新出返htc one m7複古版"},{"pid":"5fe03a11bdfbb728c72f15b9dad4f40364bf6d21","tid":907540,"uid":31405,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:34:59.000Z","msg":"王雪紅黎htc係要執左htc"